# Alembic Migrations

This directory contains Alembic migration files for the AI First CRM HCP Module database.

## Running Migrations

### Create a new migration
```bash
cd backend
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of migration"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
cd backend
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migrations
```bash
cd backend
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
cd backend
alembic history
```

### View current version
```bash
cd backend
alembic current
```
